  install minimal  Minimal WordPress installation without git repository
  install ddev     DDEV-based WordPress installation
  update           Update WordPress core and plugins (wp, default)
  mod [wp]         Modify/manage existing WordPress sites (wp, default)
  mod ddev         Modify DDEV WordPress site
  ddev update      Update DDEV WordPress site
  ddev remove      Remove DDEV containers and configuration

